{on the app} "Sometimes I picture that little hamster wheel. Ya know which one I’m talking about? The one that just goes around and around. The hamster thinks it’s going somewhere but really it’s getting nowhere and just tiring itself out. I know the feeling though! Life can totally be that way at times. We’re just 'spinning our wheels' so to speak, but we feel like we’re getting nowhere at all. We’re working and working toward something, but not actually seeing the fruits of our labor just yet. It can get tiring! This is just about the time we need to recommit that thing to Jesus, and fix our eyes on purpose." 📸 @daspenphotography a la @isaiasdcruz 💎 @kendrascott store Tampa
